<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Request for Seller Account Rejected</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333; background-color: #fff; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container {
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;
      border: 1px solid #ccc; } h1 { font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0; } p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5em; } .signature { margin-top: 1.5em; } .signature p {
      margin-bottom: 0; } .reason { margin-top: 1.5em; } .reason p {
      margin-bottom: 0.5em; } .reason h2 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom:
      0.5em; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Request for Seller Account Rejected</h1>

      <p>Dear {{username}},</p>

      <p>We regret to inform you that your request for a seller account on our
        platform has been rejected. After careful review of your application, we
        have determined that we cannot approve your request at this time.</p>

      <div class="reason">
        <h2>Reason for Rejection:</h2>
        <p>{{reason}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>We appreciate your interest in our platform and encourage you to keep
        exploring our services. Please note that this decision is final, and we
        will not be able to reconsider your application.</p>

      <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to reach out to
        us at contact@swiftmarket.com</p>

      <div class="signature">
        <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>

        <p>Sincerely,</p>

        <p>The SwiftMarket Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>